{
  "texts": [
    "7.2 Key Benefits of AI in QA AI enhances QA outcomes by making testing smarter, faster, and more resilient to change.",
    "Below are the core advantages: 1.",
    "Increased Test Coverage and Accuracy AI systems can analyze large codebases, historical defect logs, and functional specifications to generate high-volume, diverse test cases.",
    "This ensures more areas of the software are tested-especially edge cases and integration paths that human testers often overlook. 2.",
    "Faster Test Execution and Regression Cycles AI-powered test automation tools operate at machine speed."
  ]
}